v2
==
* per-var fields
    * desc (string)
    x choices (array)
    x default
    x parse (fn)

* options
    x strict (true/false) - if true, only specified args will be available
    x reporter (fn) - handle and format errors (custom one included by default)

* Misc
    x env.isProduction, env.isTesting, env.isDev
    x env must be immutable
    x play nice with the `dotenv` package
    x handle NODE_ENV automatically
    * custom parse fns
